'''争取民主变革全国协调委员会''' （{{lang-ar|هيئة التنسيق الوطنية لقوى التغيير الديمقراطي السورية}}，'''NCC'''） 是[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的一个反对派组织，领导人是Hussein Abdel Azim<ref>{{cite news|url=http://supportkurds.org/news/national-coordinating-body-for-democratic-change-names-executive-committee_syrian-opposition-must-avoid-splits/|title=National Coordinating Body for Democratic Change names Executive Committee_Syrian opposition must avoid splits|publisher=supportkurds.org|date=11 October 2011|accessdate=13 November 2011|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406122018/http://supportkurds.org/news/national-coordinating-body-for-democratic-change-names-executive-committee_syrian-opposition-must-avoid-splits/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该组织由13个[[左翼|左翼]]政党和[[独立人士|独立政治活动家]]组成，其中包括三个[[库尔德人|库尔德人]]政党以及在叙利亚国内外活动的年轻活动家<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mideast.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/11/02/meet_syrias_opposition|title=Meet Syria's Opposition|publisher=Foreign Policy|date=1 November 2011|accessdate=13 November 2011|archive-date=2013-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020182057/http://mideast.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/11/02/meet_syrias_opposition|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该组织与[[叙利亚全国委员会|叙利亚全国委员会]]是叙利亚最主要的两个反抗[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]政权的政治组织。它与全国委员会的不同点在于协调委员会认为反对派通过与叙利亚当局的对话会促使叙利亚政府主动实现“国家安全与和平地从专制向民主的转变”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syrian-opposition-still-weak-and-divided|title=Syrian Opposition Still Weak and Divided|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=18 October 2011|accessdate=13 November 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407125531/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syrian-opposition-still-weak-and-divided|archive-date=2012-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

